Here are some free websites you can use to check if your resume is ATS-friendly:

1. Jobscan - Allows you to compare your resume against job descriptions and provides feedback on ATS compatibility.

2. Resumake - Offers an ATS-friendly resume builder that ensures your resume is structured correctly.

3. Rezi - Provides an ATS optimization tool that analyzes your resume and suggests improvements.

4. SkillSyncer - Checks your resume against job postings and gives insights on how to improve ATS compatibility.

5. CVMaker - While primarily a resume builder, it also offers templates that are ATS-friendly.

